<div id="review_3224410273" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3224410273" />
    <a title="Timothy Urges" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/13015682-timothy-urges"><img alt="Timothy Urges" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1563309359p2/13015682.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3224410273?book_show_action=true">Mar 09, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Timothy Urges" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Timothy Urges" href="/user/show/13015682-timothy-urges">Timothy Urges</a>
      </span>

          added it


          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780140390032" href="/book/show/831697.Uncle_Tom_s_Cabin_or_Life_Among_the_Lowly">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3224410273" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18146174270457811146"><i>In the midst of life we are in death.</i><br/><br/>I know this is a seminal work, but oh lord I was bored. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


