      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/2478635-uncle-tom-s-cabin-or-life-among-the-lowly">Quotes from Uncle Tom&#39;s Cabin</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
